bitwarden-cli for Debian
========================

This package provides the Bitwarden CLI built from the upstream
monorepo (https://github.com/bitwarden/clients) using the OSS
(GPL-3.0) build variant.

The CLI webpack bundle is installed to /usr/lib/bitwarden-cli/
and launched via /usr/bin/bw wrapper script using the system
Node.js runtime.

Build Dependencies
------------------
This package bundles its npm dependencies as a webpack bundle
at build time. The full dependency tree is documented in
debian/copyright. See README.source for build reproduction
instructions.

Upstream
--------
CLI source: apps/cli/ in the bitwarden/clients monorepo.
License: GPL-3.0 (OSS variant, NOT the Bitwarden commercial variant).
